Wednesday, April 21, 1999

MERIT DOCKET

98-1017. State ex rel. Eckstein v. Midwest Pride IV, Inc.

Fayette App. Nos. CA97-03-007 and CA97-04-011. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed as moot.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
